h3. Issue Summary
When perming a bulk operation the "Send mail for this update" come checked by default.
 !image-2020-06-01-09-19-21-326.png|thumbnail! 

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Filter the issues that need to be done a bulk;
# In the top right, click on the three dots (*...*);
# Select "Bulk change all xx issue(s)";
# Select all the issues;
# Choose the operation;
# In the operation details, the "Send mail for this update" will be checked.

h3. Expected Results
It would be nice if "Send mail for this update" comes unchecked, as it could be a change for lots of issues and fill the user's mailbox.

h3. Actual Results

The option "Send mail for this update" comes checked by default.

h3. Workaround

Uncheck the option "Send mail for this update" manually.
